title: Preserving Individuality in Romantic Relationships
description:
Forming a shared identity as a couple can be a beautiful thing — but what happens when you feel like you’ve lost who you are? In this episode, Judah and Chelsea explore what it means to honor your individuality in a partnership, what can happen when you don't, and how you rebuild in the aftermath — both together and separately.
